{"type": "article", "id": 12934, "title": "用草做成的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-03T07:40:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060712245825VbMuSPsFNzvrYa.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自意大利的设计工作室 Henry&amp;Co 最近推出了一款特殊的椅子，这款椅子使用了一种叫做 “Ekolithos” 的材料，这种材料由枯草和青草混合回收制成，枯草坚硬可提供支撑，青草舒适温暖。这种材料因此环保而且充满自然的意味。椅子的支架采用山毛榉木，设计干净利落，十分简洁而独特。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140626InmjT7uOP6dYSGz1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140627TfldKH0t3FPuQBzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261406275x802gO4RImu7EtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140628Dy8uLnwY4eWx6XrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140628sqlLRBeEOSi625co.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}